article_id:486,category_name:Events,title_name:A New Event, Echoes of Antiquity, Is Coming Soon!,image_path:,message:<div>The Echoes of Antiquity raid event will begin <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1559282400"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>During this event, you can use co-op play to fight against the wind-attuned raid boss.</div><div><br></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/9129590fea5f2a114ceb83827483f0a5.png"></div><div>Ages ago, the Qilin tribe was at its height of prosperity. The Prince and his friends, including Qulin&#39;s own Xuan Zang, pay this mysterious tribe&#39;s village a visit on their journey to seal dangerous ancient relics. However, their progress is impeded when Xuan Zang&#39;s student, Wu Kong, gets his hands on a relic that unleashes an ancient adversary!</div><div><br></div><div>â– Notes</div><div>1. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign to participate in event quests.</div><div>2. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign in order to play co-op.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1559196000,update_time1558684609